# Financial Risk Market Capital Charge Equity Position Risk Amount

## identifier
de8140

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the market risk capital charge calculated for equity position risk, as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.CapitalChargeEquityPositionRisk.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
